I substituted a few canned chipotles in adobo for the chipotle powder. It was not nearly as subtle and may be too spicy for some, but it was a great compliment to the espresso. I also added some very dark ground Ghirardelli chocolate at the end, as I felt the espresso did not add the depth I was looking for. My guests are still raving. Enjoy!

