Rating: 3
I love black beans and couldn't wait to try this. It is quite different. At first taste, I wasn't sure about it, but day two it was awesome after the flavors had a chance to meld. The espresso sure adds a new dimension, and if anyone is curious, I ate this dish in the evening and didn't have trouble falling asleep due to the caffeine! ;-D I didn't make the polenta, but I did use store-bought polenta. I think that adds a nice layer to this dish. Also, I made half the recipe, and it was enough to last me for lunch for a week.